OL,3,CWildfires: Blaenau Gwent 'most at-risk
OL,4,Ccounty' in Wales as temperatures soar
OL,6,FBlaenau Gwent, Gwynedd and Torfaen are
OL,7,Fthe areas of Wales most at risk from
OL,8,Fwildfires but overall risk fell year-
OL,9,Fon-year, according to new research.
OL,11,FIt comes as ITV Wales has been with
OL,12,Ffirefighters near Brecon who are
OL,13,Flooking to locate water sources and
OL,14,Fhydrants to help tackle fires in hard
OL,15,Fto reach areas.
OL,17,FThe Matthews family farm near Brecon,
OL,18,Fripped through fire in the summer of
OL,19,F2022 and it was difficult to put out.
