OL,3,CWildfires: Blaenau Gwent 'most at-risk
OL,4,Ccounty' in Wales as temperatures soar
OL,6,FFarmer Andy Matthews said: "It was
OL,7,Fpretty catastrophic. It sort of raced
OL,8,Fthrough four or five fields of ripe
OL,9,Fcrop. We had seven or eight fire
OL,10,Fengines in attendance, which was a
OL,11,Fnightmare for everyone really.
OL,13,F"It was really unlucky with the
OL,14,Fweather and the circumstances. It
OL,15,Fspread like wildfire. Once they'd used
OL,16,Fthe water inside the engines, they
OL,17,Freally struggled to fill them back up
OL,18,Fagain.
