OL,3,CWildfires: Blaenau Gwent 'most at-risk
OL,4,Ccounty' in Wales as temperatures soar
OL,6,F"They had to rely on bowsers coming
OL,7,Ffrom 50 miles away to try and fill
OL,8,Fthem up, which was frustrating. It's
OL,9,Fdevastating to be honest watching all
OL,10,Fyour hard work for the year go up in
OL,11,Fsmoke."
OL,13,F"So this is the closest water supply -
OL,14,Fthe River Usk - to the farm."
OL,16,FJonathan Hodges from Mid and West
OL,17,FWales Fire and Rescue Service said:
OL,18,F"We know that we can use this (extra
OL,19,Fwater) now in the early stages of a
OL,20,Ffire."
