OL,3,CWildfires: Blaenau Gwent 'most at-risk
OL,4,Ccounty' in Wales as temperatures soar
OL,6,F"The problem we have with wildfires.
OL,7,FWe could get several on the same day.
OL,8,FBecause Wales - and particularly the
OL,9,Fcounty of Powys - is so rural, it can
OL,10,Fhave a huge drain on resources in the
OL,11,Ffact that we have to effectively have
OL,12,Fthe fire service working like a
OL,13,Fchessboard. When there's a fire we
OL,14,Fhave to move operational appliances to
OL,15,Fcover other areas. And this in itself
OL,16,Fis a challenge."
