OL,3,CWildfires: Blaenau Gwent 'most at-risk
OL,4,Ccounty' in Wales as temperatures soar
OL,6,FAntoine Halff, Co-Founder and Chief
OL,7,FAnalyst of Kayrros, the environmental
OL,8,Fintelligence company that conducted
OL,9,Fthe research, said: "The risk of
OL,10,Fwildfire remains high in Wales and
OL,11,Felsewhere, and detecting risk via
OL,12,Fsatellite insights could help to
OL,13,Fprevent unfavourable outcomes.
OL,15,F"Wildfires cause enormous damage to
OL,16,Fhuman communities, to buildings and
OL,17,Finfrastructure, and to ecosystems,' he
OL,18,Fsaid. 'The financial cost alone is eye-
OL,19,Fwatering.
