OL,3,CWildfires: Blaenau Gwent 'most at-risk
OL,4,Ccounty' in Wales as temperatures soar
OL,6,F"Though the risk of fires has fallen
OL,7,Facross Wales, they are, for the most
OL,8,Fpart, becoming more frequent and more
OL,9,Fintense when they break out.
OL,11,F"Risk at Blaenau Gwent remains
OL,12,Felevated, and risk in the few other
OL,13,Ftop five is still too high.
OL,15,F"We at Kayrros are working hard to
OL,16,Fgather, process and analyse data from
OL,17,Fsatellites and provide the resulting
OL,18,Finsights to those on the ground. They
OL,19,Fcan then take the necessary steps to
OL,20,Favoid costly damage."
